---
title: Cal Smart Middle Eastern-Inspired Double Turkey Patties with Mint Tabbouleh and Lemon Aioli
description: Fresh and herbaceous, tabbouleh is a staple in Lebanese fare. Typically made with parsley, we've adapted this version with mint. Paired with spiced turkey patties and lemon aioli, this dish is patio-ready!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-galettes-de-dinde-facon-moyen-orientale-9a62cb0f.jpg
